  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      MII Foundation is an incubator created to promote entrepreneurship and innovation. 
      We believe in providing an ecosystem where aspiring founders receive the knowledge, 
      resources, and support needed to build successful ventures.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our mission is to cultivate a community of innovators by offering mentorship from 
      experienced entrepreneurs, facilitating networking opportunities with industry leaders, 
      and providing access to critical resources. We strive to turn ambitious ideas into 
      impactful realities.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION AND VISION -->
  <section class="mission-vision-section">
    <div class="mission">
      <h3>Mission</h3>
      <p>
        Our mission is to create a dynamic platform where budding entrepreneurs can develop 
        innovative solutions and bring them to market with confidence and support.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="vision">
      <h3>Vision</h3>
      <p>
        We envision a vibrant entrepreneurial ecosystem that empowers individuals to tackle 
        real-world problems, driving economic growth and social impact.
      </p>
    </div>
